OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with any remaining
OL,7,Fheavy showers soon clearing away. The
OL,8,Frest of the night will then be largely
OL,9,Fdry with light winds, variable cloud
OL,10,Fand clear spells.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA mainly dry and bright
OL,13,Fday, perhaps the odd light shower.
OL,14,FTurning cloudier through the afternoon
OL,15,Fwith some patchy rain arriving later,
OL,16,Fpossibly heavy for a time. Freshening
OL,17,Fafternoon winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
